<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 200px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .details {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .details p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .label {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #666;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="AdvancePay Logo" class="logo">
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h2>New Demo Request Received</h2>

    <p>A new demo request has been submitted through the website. Please review the details below and follow up with the potential client.</p>

    <div class="details">
      <p><span class="label">Company Name:</span> {{companyName}}</p>
      <p><span class="label">Contact Name:</span> {{contactName}}</p>
      <p><span class="label">Email:</span> {{email}}</p>
      <p><span class="label">Phone:</span> {{phone}}</p>
      <p><span class="label">Company Size:</span> {{companySize}} employees</p>
      {{#if message}}
      <p><span class="label">Additional Information:</span><br>
      {{message}}</p>
      {{/if}}
    </div>

    <p><strong>Action Required:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>Review the request details</li>
      <li>Contact the potential client within 24 hours</li>
      <li>Schedule a demo at a convenient time</li>
      <li>Update the CRM with the demo request status</li>
    </ol>

    <p>You can access the full demo request details in the admin dashboard.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated notification. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} AdvancePay. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 